  <brief_title>Evaluation of a Third and Fourth Dose of StaphVAX® in Adults With End-Stage Renal Disease</brief_title>
  <acronym>SHIELD-2</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase 3b Multicenter, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Double-Blind Study Evaluating Immunogenicity and Safety of a 3rd and 4th Dose of StaphVAX®, a Bivalent Staphylococcus Aureus Glycoconjugate Vaccine in Adults With End-Stage Renal Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
